{"tid":2351186,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★接種專責工作小組：當局會委托大學收集市民接種後的數據，甚至主動找潛在個案","createTime":"2021-01-03T04:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T05:51:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8882fff336479c5af7754a2d98874a5ff52bb4","tid":2351186,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"疫苗接種計劃專責工作小組成員曾浩輝稱：「回看豬流感疫苗時，的確是接種後兩、三周後，當出現(注射後入院)報道，來打針的人數少了很多、差點斷了，但過了一段時間，當大家弄清楚，專家說了無關係，信心回復，接種率又開始回升。新冠疫苗是在今次新冠疫情非常重要的轉捩點，若然有足夠數目的市民接種的話，新冠疫情控制可以大大改善。」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民都關注接種後有無副作用，曾浩輝透露，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>當局會委托大學收集市民接種後的相關數據，甚至主動找潛在個案</strong></span>，他相信整個監察過程至少數個月，最長逾一年，當局亦應公開這些數據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5ff13a78335d190b12d57b06/曾浩輝料市民為健康等接種新冠疫苗-當局將監察接種後副作用\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5ff13a78335d190b12d57b06%2F%E6%9B%BE%E6%B5%A9%E8%BC%9D%E6%96%99%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%82%BA%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%AD%89%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%87%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E5%BE%8C%E5%89%AF%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0K2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=18ebfedf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5ff13a78335d190b12d57b06/曾浩輝料市民為健康等接種新冠疫苗-當局將監察接種後副作用</a>"},{"pid":"e336eff15a2e259dea0c80a97bfc3d58fdc07cb2","tid":2351186,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157baf4784860d64633c69